PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of CLAUDETTE TESSIER-COUTURE, of Ville Lac Saint-Joseph, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Ports Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term ending December 31, 1999, in the place of Michel Bérubé, whose term has expired.
